11	 *     file, the harness creates a fresh H5R_ref_t pointing at that object
12	 *     (object reference) and, for datasets, a region reference over a
13	 *     minimal hyperslab.  It then calls H5Rget_obj_type3 and
14	 *     H5Ropen_object / H5Ropen_region to resolve those references, which
15	 *     exercises the library's file-offset arithmetic.
16	 *
17	 *  2. RAW DEREFERENCE  — if the fuzz file contains a dataset whose element
18	 *     type is H5T_STD_REF (the new packed-reference type), the harness reads
19	 *     the raw reference bytes from that dataset and dereferences each one.
20	 *     Those bytes come directly from the fuzzer, so any offset/address
21	 *     arithmetic done during resolution is performed on attacker-controlled
22	 *     data.
