56	 * Exercises H5Rget_obj_type3, H5Ropen_object, H5Ropen_region.
57	 * The caller is responsible for calling H5Rdestroy on the ref afterwards
58	 * (unless the ref was read from a dataset, in which case H5Rdestroy must
59	 * still be called after this function).
60	 */
61	static void
